  "slug": "easy-anvils",
  "title": "Easy Anvils",
  "description": "Overhauled anvils with stored items, fairer costs, and no more frustrating repair penalties.",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/easyanvils/banner.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/easyanvils/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 36px;\"><a href=\"https://lunapixel.studio/discord\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Discord&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"117\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://x.com/Fusseel\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Twitter&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=x&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"116\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@heyitsfuzs\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=YouTube&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=youtube&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"118\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/Fuzss\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=GitHub&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=github&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"108\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/fuzs_\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=CurseForge&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"143\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Fuzs\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Modrinth&amp;color=ECEBE6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=modrinth&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"129\" height=\"28\" /></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/easyanvils/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/about.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Easy Anvils</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> makes anvils more convenient, less frustrating, and far more practical to use. 🔨 Items stay inside the interface when you close it, while the contents are rendered directly on the block for a more immersive experience.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">The mod also reworks several vanilla anvil mechanics that can make repairing and upgrading gear unnecessarily tedious. Prior work penalties become much less restrictive, repair costs stay reasonable for longer, and several common actions are made more affordable. ✨</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">From repairing damaged anvils to free renaming and formatting support, this mod delivers a collection of quality-of-life improvements that make anvils feel better throughout the entire game.</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/easyanvils/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/features.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🔨 </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Persistent Anvils:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Items remain inside the anvil after closing the interface instead of popping back into your inventory.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">👀 </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Visible Contents:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Items placed in an anvil are rendered directly on the block in the world.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">📉 </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Reduced Prior Work Penalties:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Repairing and renaming no longer suffer from rapidly escalating prior work costs.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">✨ </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">More Affordable Enchanting:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Enchanted book application costs are reduced and expensive operations are far less restrictive.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🏷️ </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Free Renaming:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Renaming items can be performed without spending experience levels.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🎨 </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Formatting Support:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Item names support formatting codes for custom colors and text styles.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🛠️ </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Repair Damaged Anvils:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Use iron blocks to restore anvils and extend their lifespan.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">💪 </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">More Durable Anvils:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Anvils are less likely to become damaged or break during use.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⚙️ </span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Highly Configurable:</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> Fine tune repair costs, prior work penalties, durability, and many other mechanics.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/easyanvils/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/media.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/easyanvils/media/1.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"480\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/easyanvils/media/2.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"480\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/easyanvils/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/installation.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⏩ </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">INSTALLATION REQUIRED ON CLIENT &amp; REQUIRED ON SERVER</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⏩ </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">REQUIRES </span></strong><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/puzzles-lib\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">PUZZLES LIB</span></strong></a><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> TO BE INSTALLED (FABRIC &amp; NEOFORGE)</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⏩ </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">REQUIRES </span></strong><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">FABRIC API</span></strong></a><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> TO BE INSTALLED (FABRIC)</span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">⏩ </span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">REQUIRES </span></strong><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/forge-config-api-port\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">FORGE CONFIG API PORT</span></strong></a><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> TO BE INSTALLED (FABRIC)</span></strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/easyanvils/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/configuration.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">If available for a mod, configuration is possible directly from in-game using the mod menu (requires </span><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/modmenu\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Mod Menu</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> by </span><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Prospector\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Prospector</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> to be installed on Fabric).</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">For manual configuration using an external text editor all files are found at </span><code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">.minecraft/config</span></code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">, named as </span><code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">MOD_ID-client.toml</span></code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">, </span><code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">MOD_ID-common.toml</span></code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">, or </span><code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">MOD_ID-server.toml</span></code><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">, depending on the type of config. Not all types might exist for a mod, if any at all.</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/easyanvils/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/credits.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"32\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🌟 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Thanks to </span><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/tfarecnim\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">tfarecnim</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> and their </span><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/anvil-tweaks\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Anvil Tweaks</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">, and </span><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/anvil-repair\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Anvil Repair</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> mods, which this mod is largely based upon.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🌟 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Thanks to </span><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/elhertz\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">elhertz</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> for suggesting the anvil max enchantment level fix.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">🌟 </span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Thanks to </span><a href=\"https://github.com/Illios42\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Illios42</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"> for suggesting the feature for allowing text to be stylized using Minecraft's formatting codes in the anvil and name tag interface.</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/easyanvils/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/illager-invasion\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/illagerinvasion/banner.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></a></p><p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/stylish-effects\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/stylisheffects/banner.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></a></p><p><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/armored-foes\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/armoredfoes/banner.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></a></p><p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/easyanvils/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://lunapixel.studio/discord\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/studio.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/data/easyanvils/strip.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n",
